1
00:00:11,260 --> 00:00:12,060
Xiyin.

2
00:00:12,540 --> 00:00:14,100
Do you still blame me?

3
00:00:15,900 --> 00:00:16,980
I wouldn't dare.

4
00:00:17,900 --> 00:00:18,900
Do you know

5
00:00:19,300 --> 00:00:21,260
why the Shadow Clan keeps attacking?

6
00:00:21,900 --> 00:00:23,660
Because possessing Xieyun

7
00:00:24,180 --> 00:00:26,940
means gaining the power
to destroy the world.

8
00:00:28,580 --> 00:00:31,700
I know you went to the Juxian Cave
to find another way.

9
00:00:32,340 --> 00:00:33,140
But this

10
00:00:33,740 --> 00:00:36,020
is not a solution.

11
00:00:38,500 --> 00:00:39,300
Immortal Venerable.

12
00:00:40,780 --> 00:00:42,500
Do we really have to sacrifice Yang?

13
00:00:43,700 --> 00:00:45,580
As long as Xieyun exists,

14
00:00:45,900 --> 00:00:49,140
that boy will forever be the target
of the Shadow Clan.

15
00:00:51,500 --> 00:00:52,300
Unless...

16
00:00:53,540 --> 00:00:54,500
Unless what?

17
00:00:56,300 --> 00:00:57,100
Unless

18
00:00:58,460 --> 00:01:00,460
an immortal sacrifices their spirit

19
00:01:01,460 --> 00:01:03,300
to seal the Shadow Clan away forever.

20
00:01:03,940 --> 00:01:04,860
Only then

21
00:01:05,500 --> 00:01:07,260
will Yang be truly safe.

22
00:01:20,820 --> 00:01:23,880
[Immortal Beyond Dust]
[Episode 21]

23
00:01:34,700 --> 00:01:35,620
Your wine spilled.

24
00:01:36,260 --> 00:01:37,540
Let me get you some more.

25
00:01:37,540 --> 00:01:38,500
No need.

26
00:01:56,300 --> 00:01:57,460
Have you ever

27
00:01:58,100 --> 00:02:00,020
been betrayed by someone closest to you?

28
00:02:07,700 --> 00:02:08,500
He actually

29
00:02:12,900 --> 00:02:14,540
cares about you a lot.

30
00:02:17,500 --> 00:02:18,540
Are you saying

31
00:02:19,140 --> 00:02:20,500
I misunderstood him?

32
00:02:24,060 --> 00:02:24,980
Tu Jing,

33
00:02:25,260 --> 00:02:26,700
you're too naive.

34
00:02:28,140 --> 00:02:29,940
There are things
you haven't experienced,

35
00:02:30,500 --> 00:02:31,700
so you wouldn't understand.

36
00:02:32,700 --> 00:02:34,500
Sacrifice?

37
00:02:35,860 --> 00:02:37,460
It's just an excuse.

38
00:02:54,620 --> 00:02:55,460
It's getting late.

39
00:02:56,380 --> 00:02:57,180
Stop drinking.

40
00:02:57,660 --> 00:02:58,820
Let me help you back to rest.

41
00:02:59,540 --> 00:03:00,500
Leave me alone.

42
00:03:40,060 --> 00:03:41,140
I actually

43
00:03:42,060 --> 00:03:43,900
have some of your memories.

44
00:03:45,380 --> 00:03:46,180
So,

45
00:03:47,300 --> 00:03:48,940
you sacrificed so much

46
00:03:49,500 --> 00:03:51,300
for that fool.

47
00:03:52,340 --> 00:03:54,100
I won't be as utterly stupid

48
00:03:55,020 --> 00:03:56,740
as you were.

49
00:04:07,340 --> 00:04:08,140
Yang.

50
00:04:32,420 --> 00:04:33,740
With these demon cores,

51
00:04:34,220 --> 00:04:36,260
I can finally repair the Fushi Mirror.

52
00:04:37,940 --> 00:04:39,300
To fix the Fushi Mirror,

53
00:04:39,780 --> 00:04:41,580
you'd just take innocent lives?

54
00:04:43,860 --> 00:04:44,660
Yes.

55
00:04:45,140 --> 00:04:46,780
If it means repairing the Fushi Mirror,

56
00:04:47,740 --> 00:04:50,340
a few vile demons won't matter!

57
00:05:09,660 --> 00:05:10,020
Yaoyang?

58
00:05:13,220 --> 00:05:14,580
Did Ruoxi come here?

59
00:05:15,180 --> 00:05:16,220
She

60
00:05:16,900 --> 00:05:17,780
was here.

61
00:05:18,300 --> 00:05:19,500
Did she meet Gu Li?

62
00:05:19,860 --> 00:05:21,180
What did they talk about?

63
00:05:21,740 --> 00:05:22,540
Yes,

64
00:05:23,100 --> 00:05:23,900
they met.

65
00:05:24,380 --> 00:05:25,500
They talked about some kind of deal.

66
00:05:25,700 --> 00:05:26,500
What deal?

67
00:05:26,780 --> 00:05:27,460
I didn't catch

68
00:05:27,860 --> 00:05:28,940
the details.

69
00:05:31,260 --> 00:05:32,060
Yaoyang.

70
00:05:32,500 --> 00:05:33,260
there's something

71
00:05:33,860 --> 00:05:35,180
I've never told you.

72
00:05:35,700 --> 00:05:36,340
Miss Ruoxi

73
00:05:36,780 --> 00:05:38,380
came to see me before.

74
00:05:41,140 --> 00:05:42,780
Yaoyang wouldn't let me tell you!

75
00:05:46,020 --> 00:05:46,980
Okay. Fine.

76
00:05:47,260 --> 00:05:48,340
To be honest with you,

77
00:05:48,540 --> 00:05:49,700
he's been sustaining your life

78
00:05:50,100 --> 00:05:51,660
by using his heart's blood

79
00:05:51,900 --> 00:05:52,740
to nurture the Gu.

80
00:05:53,700 --> 00:05:54,260
As a result,

81
00:05:54,700 --> 00:05:55,980
the Gu poison has seeped into his heart.

82
00:05:56,500 --> 00:05:57,380
He probably

83
00:05:58,260 --> 00:05:59,460
doesn't have much time left.

84
00:05:59,500 --> 00:06:00,500
What did you say?

85
00:06:02,460 --> 00:06:03,300
He actually...

86
00:06:05,260 --> 00:06:06,300
Why didn't you tell me sooner?

87
00:06:06,300 --> 00:06:07,500
She wouldn't let me tell you!

88
00:06:07,500 --> 00:06:08,540
And I told you not to tell her!

89
00:06:19,660 --> 00:06:21,980
You're already this weak.

90
00:06:22,500 --> 00:06:24,700
Why push yourself to come see me?

91
00:06:24,900 --> 00:06:25,900
What kind of deal

92
00:06:26,980 --> 00:06:28,300
do you have with Ruoxi?

93
00:06:28,540 --> 00:06:29,140
What,

94
00:06:29,500 --> 00:06:30,900
she didn't tell you?

95
00:06:31,700 --> 00:06:33,260
But that doesn't matter anymore.

96
00:06:34,260 --> 00:06:35,900
I've already repaired the Fushi Mirror.

97
00:06:36,340 --> 00:06:37,100
I'm one step closer

98
00:06:37,540 --> 00:06:38,900
to my plan.

99
00:06:38,980 --> 00:06:40,100
You promised me

100
00:06:40,460 --> 00:06:41,500
you'd save her.

101
00:06:41,500 --> 00:06:42,900
How could you be so naive

102
00:06:43,460 --> 00:06:45,100
and actually trust
someone else's promise?

103
00:06:55,340 --> 00:06:56,140
Xinghong.

104
00:06:56,780 --> 00:06:58,300
Have you found the Fushi Mirror?

105
00:06:59,460 --> 00:07:00,260
Immortal Venerable,

106
00:07:00,900 --> 00:07:02,260
just as you expected,

107
00:07:02,660 --> 00:07:04,300
the Fushi Mirror is indeed
with the Shadow Clan.

108
00:07:05,500 --> 00:07:07,340
The Shadow Clan is greedy by nature.

109
00:07:07,900 --> 00:07:09,860
They are bound to make a comeback.

110
00:07:10,660 --> 00:07:11,740
Spread the order.

111
00:07:12,500 --> 00:07:13,180
All disciples

112
00:07:13,180 --> 00:07:15,780
must be on high alert in the coming days.

113
00:07:16,300 --> 00:07:17,700
No carelessness is allowed.

114
00:07:18,740 --> 00:07:19,660
Understood.

115
00:07:20,580 --> 00:07:21,700
And the Fushi Mirror...?

116
00:07:54,060 --> 00:07:55,340
You're awake already?

117
00:07:55,580 --> 00:07:57,300
Have you found out something?

118
00:08:01,100 --> 00:08:02,140
You guessed right.

119
00:08:03,180 --> 00:08:04,180
I have indeed found out

120
00:08:04,780 --> 00:08:05,700
some

121
00:08:05,900 --> 00:08:07,500
of your secrets.

122
00:08:12,340 --> 00:08:13,380
The Soul Vessel is missing.

123
00:08:16,340 --> 00:08:17,140
Tell me,

124
00:08:17,500 --> 00:08:19,100
where have you hidden
my master's immortal soul?

125
00:08:19,260 --> 00:08:20,820
I've hidden it

126
00:08:21,540 --> 00:08:23,340
somewhere you'll never find.

127
00:08:23,700 --> 00:08:24,540
Just give up.

128
00:08:25,340 --> 00:08:26,100
You'll never

129
00:08:26,700 --> 00:08:28,700
turn me into your master!

130
00:08:29,500 --> 00:08:30,340
So you already know.

131
00:08:36,100 --> 00:08:39,300
Only when
all of Bai Xiyin's souls dissipate

132
00:08:39,900 --> 00:08:41,300
can I

133
00:08:42,180 --> 00:08:43,980
forever be myself.

134
00:08:45,060 --> 00:08:45,980
Give her back to me!

135
00:08:48,060 --> 00:08:49,180
In your dreams.

136
00:08:50,260 --> 00:08:51,740
Unless you kill me.

137
00:08:55,180 --> 00:08:55,980
But

138
00:08:56,540 --> 00:08:58,380
could you really do it?

139
00:09:10,740 --> 00:09:11,660
You and her

140
00:09:13,980 --> 00:09:16,060
are worlds apart.

141
00:09:23,340 --> 00:09:24,140
Leave.

142
00:09:24,900 --> 00:09:26,300
I don't want to see you again.

143
00:09:26,900 --> 00:09:28,260
What a devoted disciple,

144
00:09:28,580 --> 00:09:31,100
so attached to your master.

145
00:09:32,660 --> 00:09:33,460
Bai Ruoxi!

146
00:09:34,700 --> 00:09:35,460
What are you doing?

147
00:09:38,780 --> 00:09:39,660
You

148
00:09:40,180 --> 00:09:42,380
want your master's soul so badly.

149
00:09:43,580 --> 00:09:44,940
Then I'll grant your wish.

150
00:09:45,860 --> 00:09:47,500
Bai Ruoxi, let me go!

151
00:09:49,100 --> 00:09:49,900
Stop!

152
00:10:00,380 --> 00:10:01,580
Bai Ruoxi, are you insane?

153
00:10:02,220 --> 00:10:03,260
Don't you

154
00:10:04,140 --> 00:10:06,220
want your master's soul?

155
00:10:06,460 --> 00:10:07,700
I'll give it to you now.

156
00:10:12,100 --> 00:10:13,500
Stop this!

157
00:10:22,980 --> 00:10:23,780
Get out!

158
00:10:25,220 --> 00:10:26,300
I don't want to see you again.

159
00:10:27,700 --> 00:10:28,340
You think

160
00:10:28,660 --> 00:10:30,300
I want to be here with you?

161
00:11:07,940 --> 00:11:10,680
♪What is flickering?♪

162
00:11:10,900 --> 00:11:13,420
♪Shining, delicate, and bright♪

163
00:11:13,580 --> 00:11:19,420
♪Like a trace of bitterness in a smile♪

164
00:11:19,460 --> 00:11:22,300
♪What is falling?♪

165
00:11:22,740 --> 00:11:25,540
♪Clean, precise, and light♪

166
00:11:25,780 --> 00:11:30,980
♪Like enduring too many farewells♪

167
00:11:31,900 --> 00:11:33,500
♪When petals drift down♪

168
00:11:33,540 --> 00:11:35,000
♪When the rain falls all around♪

169
00:11:35,100 --> 00:11:37,700
♪I gaze into your eyes♪

170
00:11:37,860 --> 00:11:39,560
♪Beyond the dunes♪

171
00:11:39,660 --> 00:11:40,940
♪No end in sight♪

172
00:11:40,940 --> 00:11:43,940
♪I am like a mayfly♪

173
00:11:44,100 --> 00:11:45,500
♪I won't ask what the future holds♪

174
00:11:45,540 --> 00:11:47,000
♪Nor will I run away♪

175
00:11:47,020 --> 00:11:49,960
♪Through all seasons by my side♪

176
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:55,220
♪Searching for sparks in the dust♪

177
00:12:09,540 --> 00:12:12,280
♪What is flickering?♪

178
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:14,980
♪Shining, delicate, and bright♪

179
00:12:15,180 --> 00:12:20,980
♪Like a trace of bitterness in a smile♪

180
00:12:21,420 --> 00:12:24,220
♪What is falling?♪

181
00:12:24,340 --> 00:12:27,160
♪Clean, precise, and light♪

182
00:12:27,380 --> 00:12:32,380
♪Like enduring too many farewells♪

183
00:12:33,500 --> 00:12:34,980
♪When petals drift down♪

184
00:12:34,980 --> 00:12:36,480
♪When the rain falls all around♪

185
00:12:36,580 --> 00:12:39,140
♪I gaze into your eyes♪
